Using the formula: n = 4, so -4/2 = -2. 

All methods give the same result. 

Another test: 1 - 2 + 3 - 4 + 5 - 6. 

Pairing: (1 - 2) + (3 - 4) + (5 - 6) = (-1) + (-1) + (-1) = -3. 

